desc: This spoon is a grid based launcher/switcher for applications.  It uses your Dock applications and running applications as the source.  Apps are chosen using a grid based chording system.
doc:
The selected application, by chording, will either be launched or brought to the front.
Official homepage for more info and documentation:
[https://github.com/Maahsome/Spoons](https://github.com/Maahsome/Spoons)
